fields.name: Vyber Ride E1 Special Edition M7
fields.description: This is the award-winning Vyber Ride E1 Special Edition M7 2022 Women. You have probably been told that this bicycle has been assessed as an economical choice by the ANWB in 2021. And we understand that this e-bike has received that label!

fields.name: Stromer ST1 2021 Sport
fields.description: The Stromer ST1 may be the entry-level model of this Swiss E-bike builder, but it is absolutely no laughing matter. This ST1 is like a tank on the road and has everything you expect in an E-bike in this price category, and more! The Swiss engineers have done their best to make this electric bike look as sleek as possible, which means that all cabling is integrated into the frame and all parts are painted in clean, clear colors. Also on this model are only parts from A-brands and top quality.

fields.name: Le Velo Nancy 2022 Women
fields.description: Want to make the most beautiful rides by bike? The Le Velo Nancy is the e-bike that combines comfort with sporty handling. This bike has a comfortable, upright sitting position and a powerful motor with a torque of 80 Nm. As a result, the Nancy rides very smoothly and when the circumstances call for it, this bike goes up a gear

fields.name: Bird Bike A Frame 2022 Men
fields.description: The Bird Bike is an urban e-bike par excellence, a modern design that fits perfectly into urban life but also looks particularly good in the more rural environment. Bird's electric bicycles are designed with stylish simplicity in mind, which is reflected in the modern shapes and seamless design. The Bird Bike 2022 also received the prize best tested in the category of electric sporty commuter bicycle up to €2,500 during the AD Bicycle Test 2022.

fields.name: Cube Touring Hybrid One 400 2022 Men
fields.description: The Cube Touring Hybrid One is equipped to a high standard for a very competitive price. No other e-bike in this price range has a Bosch Performance Line with an integrated battery. The torque of 65Nm makes it possible to drive very sporty. The battery of 400Wh is sufficient for the medium-long distances, but for the real mile-eaters this will be just a bit too little

fields.name: Sticker Y Muse 45 2022
fields.description: The Klever Y Muse 2022 has won the prize best buy in the category Speed Pedelecs from €5,000 during the AD Bicycle Test 2022 ! And there are more reasons to buy the Klever Y Muse 2022. Thanks to the smaller wheels and the smaller frame, this speed pedelec is also ideal for smaller people or people with limited mobility. This makes the Y muse unique in the speed pedelec segment, because most other speed pedelecs often have a sportier frame with a higher step

fields.name: Popal Daily Dutch Prestige-E F3 2022 Women
fields.description: Anyone looking for an electric transport bike will soon come across the Popal Daily Dutch Prestige-E. This versatile e-bike can now be seen in many cities and in many schoolyards. Popal has equipped the Prestige-E with a 470Wh large battery, so you can ride this bike for quite some time. The Prestige-E series is very comfortable because of the luxurious saddle. In addition, the bike steers lightly and smoothly. This is very convenient if a basket or crate is mounted on the front carrier.

fields.name: Super73 ZX 2022
fields.description: You want to be seen on this bike. This Super73 ZX is made to make an everyday ride special. Thanks to the comfortable seat height and the wide tires, you will experience the ultimate cruise feeling. The Super73 ZX is equipped with 10-speed Shimano gears and is therefore also very suitable for simply making good kilometers. The 615Wh battery is nicely integrated under the saddle, so that the bike not only looks clean, you can also cycle many kilometers on it.

fields.name: Sticker X Speed Original 45 20211
fields.description: The Klever X Speed Original offers the best price-quality ratio if you are looking for a speed pedelec that really travels 45 km/h. A great bike that scored no less than 8.3 in the category speed pedelecs up to €5,000 from Fietstest.nl 2021

fields.name: Specialized S-WORKS EPIC Carbon
fields.description: If speed could talk, it would introduce itself as the totally the Specialized S-Works Epic. The S-Work Epic offers 100mm of brilliantly efficient BRAIN-controlled travel. Combined with the increased rear stiffness, this results in unparalleled power transfer.

fields.name: FOCUS SAM Carbon Mountainbike
fields.description: The JAM is FOCUS' 170mm Enduro Fully. Thanks to a super light and durable carbon structure, the complete SAM frameset weighs only 2270 g. With the perfect mix of High Modulus (high stiffness) and High Strength (high strength) carbon fibres, FOCUS offer the best ratio of minimum weight with maximum strength for demanding trail use. The FOCUS tests ensure maximum strength, which is well above standard.

fields.name: FOCUS JAM
fields.description: The JAM is the 150mm all-mountain trail fully of FOCUS. With its playful and intuitive character, you get the most fun out of every ride. Agile and direct handling merges with a lot of safety resources of the chassis providing confidence and joy on any downhill. You are perfectly seated in the middle of the mountain bike to control any situation and to easily pedal up all the steep hills on your ride

fields.name: CUBE ACID
fields.description: With the brand-new Acid, CUBE reckon it's time to reassess how good you think a trail hardtail can be. CUBE started with SRAM's NX Eagle 1x12 transmission, because it has the range and performance you'll need for off-road adventures

fields.name: BMC TWOSTROKE AL THREE
fields.description: The BMC Twostroke AL comes with a refined aluminium frame that takes ist heritage from the race proven Fourstroke and crosses it with a fighter jet inspired design, to create the perfect blend of performance, functionality and aesthetics.

fields.name: Ghost RIOT AM AL U Essential
fields.description: The brandnew Ghost RIOT AM follows in the footsteps of its predecessor - yet only its name has remained the same. If you have high mountains in view and are ready to earn your downhill, this muscle-driven all mountain bike is the perfect choice for you. The SuperFit geometry puts you in the perfect position to tackle long climbs comfortably and efficiently

fields.name: Santa Cruz HIGHTOWER C R NX
fields.description: Since its introduction, the Hightower has been the most versatile trail bike from the Santa Cruz portfolio. It is more agile than its big suspension brother Megatower, but more confident in technical terrain than its fast cousin Tallboy. The Hightower scores where the trails are long and challenging and steep climbs are rewarded with real descents. The lower baffle-controlled VPP shock creates a near-linear spring curve, absorbing shocks of all sizes while still maintaining progressivity!

fields.name: Specialized TARMAC SL7 PRO - Force eTap AXS
fields.description: Specialized designed the Tarmac to provide the perfect blend of aerodynamics, light weight and ride quality to give you the future rides of your life. From using the FreeFoil Shape Library to design the best tube shapes to developing the Rider First Engineered generation, the Tarmac is the culmination of an everlasting pursuit of speed. It's a thoroughbred race machine without compromise. Your bike to leave them all behind.

fields.name: Cannondale SUPERSIX EVO Hi-MOD Disc
fields.description: A pure road bike. Light, smooth and ultra fast. The evolution of the classic race machine. 30 watts. That's how much power the drag-reducing tube shapes and integrated design of the new SuperSix EVO saves over the prior version at 30 mph (48.3 km/h).

fields.name: Basso Diamante SV Chorus Roadbike
fields.description: Creating the fastest version of that fantastic ride quality was the objective behind the project that would add the letters SV to the Diamante. The resulting model saw every square milimeter of its design dedicated to the embodiment of the acronym for SUPER VELOCE. Translated, it means SUPER FAST…but through meticulous research and development since its its release, now becomes SUPER FASTER

fields.name: BMC TEAMMACHINE SLR01 FOUR - Force eTap AXS
fields.description: 10 years ago, BMC launched a bike that kickstarted a revolution in the design and construction of the performance road bike. The Teammachine SLR, has won every major title that a bike can win including; Monuments, World Championships, Olympic Games and the Tour de France.

fields.name: CUBE KATHMANDU SL - Trekking Bike - 2022
fields.description: Completely redesigned for 2022, CUBE have taken everything that's good about the Kathmandu and made it even better. So, for example, the reworked Integrated Carrier 3.0 is designed to work seamlessly with the Acid mudguards. CUBE have fitted a flat mount for the rear disc brake - it also accommodates the kickstand - and used Smooth Welding to give the frame joints a tidy, organic appearance.

fields.name: Rennstahl 853 Pinion - 650B Trekking Bike
fields.description: Rennstahl has a mission - to build the best touring bike in the world. The Pinion is extremely solid and reliable, a true expedition bike. Almost all components are made in Germany, representing the possibilities of state-of-the-art engineering. Also extremely durable and almost maintenance-free is the Pinion gear shift and the toothed belt used. The frame geometry with the sloping top tube allows for a wide range of legroom and seating positions from sporty stretched to comfortable upright. The gearbox and lighting system are colour-coordinated for a beautiful look

fields.name: Giant TOURER LDS - Easy Entry City Bike
fields.description: With the Giant Tourer you always cut a fine figure. Leave the others in the traffic jam on the left and pass or recover from the workday and train on an extensive tour. With the modern city bikes from GAINT, it's up to you.

fields.name: Continental Tire Ride Tour 28 x 1 3/8 x 1 5/8
fields.description: Continental Tire Ride Tour

fields.name: AMIGO Tire M-700 28 x 1.75 brown
fields.description: With this wear-resistant tire from AMIGO you have a lot of grip on paved roads in dry and wet weather. The tire has been developed and produced with care, so that you enjoy the best quality for a competitive price

fields.name: AMIGO Tire M-700 28 x 1.75 blue
fields.description: With this wear-resistant tire from AMIGO you have a lot of grip on paved roads in dry and wet weather. The tire has been developed and produced with care, so that you enjoy the best quality for a competitive price

fields.name: Triple crankset 7, 8 and 9 gears
fields.description: For 7 to 9 speed transmission, square insert, length min 113 and max 119 mm

fields.name: Dunlop Double Pannier - 30 x 36 x 12 cm
fields.description: A bicycle bag is so very handy. Especially this Dunlop double pannier. With its generous dimensions of 30 x 36 x 12 cm per bag, you can store everything in it. The messages for example. You can also put things in it that you need during a bike ride. A raincoat, food and drink, an umbrella and, for example, a bicycle repair kit.

fields.name: Phone holder Bicycle - Smartphone holder - Universal - Up to 7 Inch- bike
fields.description: Do you often ride your bike and still want to be able to use your phone safely? Then you must have this phone holder for your bicycle. Thanks to the handy attachment, the phone holder can be mounted on the handlebar in a few moments without the need for tools. Place the phone in the holder and turn the knob on the back of the phone holder to secure the phone. Due to the smart design, the phone holder can be rotated 360° degrees and can be adjusted to any desired angle.

fields.name: AGU Solid Cycling Jersey III Trend Men - Brown
fields.description: Ride in style in this comfortable cycling jersey made from high-quality fabrics. The 4-way stretch material gives you the ultimate freedom of movement.
